QuestData.Title: Old Nasha's Paw
QuestData.Description:
The old bear's paw is sticky with honey. She likely ransacked a number of hives before you stopped her.
The Hivemother will be interested in this item.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take Old Nasha's paw to the Honeyback Hivemother for a reward.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Take Old Nasha's paw to the Honeyback Hivemother for a reward.
